    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Diagrams that represent open or closed figures that are not necessarily plane and that take a form as if a rope or cord were acted upon at a number of points by forces acting in various directions. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
